                <note rend="inline" type="source">819.51A/14: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Panama</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Price</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-04-04T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 4, 1921—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>32. Your 81, March 31, 2 p.m.</p>
                <p>Department hopes that Ruan’s new contract will be signed without delay and that
                    changes therein to which you refer do not alter the main conditions which have
                    hitherto determined the nature of the services to be rendered to Panaman
                    Government by Fiscal Agent. Please notify Department by cable as soon as
                    contract has been signed</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
